To be clear: https://www.facebook.com/?_rdr is the production domain of Facebook. That is not open source, and the core codebase of Facebook is not publicly available for cloning due to proprietary licensing and security restrictions.

However, you can build a framework that mimics Facebook Lite UI/UX and integrates AGI enhancements under your project: Facebook Lite Plus, using open-source tech stacks.


